  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In patients undergoing spinal anesthesia, the investigators used an Infra-red camera and a
      respiratory volume monitor to determine the accuracy of the ventilation rate of the infra red
      camera by measuring the respiratory rate, ventilation volume, and ventilation volume with
      respiratory volume monitor.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
